{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a doctor sitting on a chair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people went through the barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the end of the barrack, he would select the people, in or out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was in front of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was behind him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a few people were-- I always tried to put myself between people that were of smaller stature than my father, so that I wasn't dwarfed, that my [? size ?] wasn't so apparent.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but it didn't help, because we were naked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He examined us naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by that time, I was already skinnier-- [DRINKS] And I was rejected.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they separated us with some kapos keeping guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, my father, with the people that were selected, were sitting-- standing to one side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father saw the officer was, obviously, supervising this selection, in addition to the doctor, who was doing the-- the actual selecting.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he went over to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He tried to go over to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, the-- the-- there was a policeman-- or, I mean, it was a kapo, or-- or a Nazi soldier that was there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They tried to stop him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he started to hassle-- hassle with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And finally, this officer saw this commotion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he-- he motioned to my father to come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was dressed by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he says, I have a son here, and I would like him to come with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I understand we're going to a factory to work something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He's an electrician.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He's a good mechanic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He's 17 years old, and I would like to have him with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
